</style><p>3月22日，在世界棒球经典赛（WBC）的决赛中，军道米玲在自己的官方推特上写道：“<em>这是一个投球手，如果一个强壮的人站起来朝他的头或身体扔，他会参与。你不能阻止它吗？</em> ”推特上建议给击球手一个死球。对此，“这不是不了解棒球规则的问题”、“这是一个人的道德问题”、“ANYCOLOR应该先教育自己的人才，然后再采取反诽谤措施”等批评声接踵而至。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="XXDIknRLgJ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-criticized-for-problematic-comments-during-wbc-live-streaming/">VTuber Gundo Mirei WBC直播中有问题言论遭多方批评 各家媒体纷纷报道</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Gunmichi Mirei在WBC直播时的言论被批，各家媒体纷纷报道”——P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-criticized-for-problematic-comments-during-wbc-live-streaming/embed/#?secret=OTyiaUBwI5#?secret=XXDIknRLgJ" data-secret="XXDIknRLgJ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此后，ANYCOLOR于3月23日宣布Gundo先生将被禁止活动。这种处置一直持续到 6 月 19 日。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="2luZczLpF0"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-suspends-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-due-to-problematic-comments-about-world-baseball-classic/">ANYCOLOR Inc. Nijisanji VTuber Mirei Gundo 被暂停活动，提及他过去的行为也不合适</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR Inc. Nijisanji VTuber Mirei Gundo 因活动被停职并提到他过去的行为不当” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-suspends-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-due-to-problematic-comments-about-world-baseball-classic/embed/#?secret=GbSgmbI0fA#?secret=2luZczLpF0" data-secret="2luZczLpF0" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>关于京藤先生，据说他的行为在过去是有问题的（肯定法西斯主义的言论，VTubers 很快就会过时的言论，挪用大阪排球协会的钱等给属于 VTuber 办公室 Hololive Production 的人才）但是，一些媒体和所谓的摘要网站，曝光YouTuber等都在批评，说“ <em>ANYCOLOR在给我优惠</em>”。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="hehk2ACae3"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-gundo-mirei-revealed-in-a-dating-statement/">Nijisanji附属VTuber“Mirei Gundo”提到过去约会Sakura act的言论</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nijisanji 附属的 VTuber “Mirei Gundo”指的是过去约会樱花行为” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-gundo-mirei-revealed-in-a-dating-statement/embed/#?secret=Ox0JuRQ8EC#?secret=hehk2ACae3" data-secret="hehk2ACae3" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="hbn58T4nlI"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-spread-the-word-the-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-who-is-under-suspension-for-her-activities-shows-no-remorse/">部分汇总网站``VTuber Gundo Mirei的表演者/被拘留的声音模型无法反映&#39;&#39;</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“部分总结网站``VTuber Gundo Mirei的表演者/声音模型暂停活动，没有看到悔恨&#39;&#39;” - P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-spread-the-word-the-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-who-is-under-suspension-for-her-activities-shows-no-remorse/embed/#?secret=4GjcVsFy61#?secret=hbn58T4nlI" data-secret="hbn58T4nlI" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="M3VyFQae1L"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-unfamiliarity-with-baseball-rules-attitude-is-raising-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/">VTuber Mirei Gundo质疑“我不懂棒球规则” 部分言论指的是过去的职业棒球选手</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Mirei Gunmichi 对“我不知道棒球规则”表示怀疑，并发表言论指的是过去的前职业棒球运动员” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-unfamiliarity-with-baseball-rules-attitude-is-raising-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/embed/#?secret=6XQkS7Tex4#?secret=M3VyFQae1L" data-secret="M3VyFQae1L" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Z5gzFd4OrL"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-media-outlets-began-to-pursue-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-past-behavior-including-50000-yen-super-chat-demand-problem/">部分媒体追究二三寺VTuber Mirei Gundo的“过去行为” 50,000日元spacha请求问题</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“部分媒体 Nijisanji VTuber Gundo Mirei 的“过去行为”50,000 日元 spacha 请求问题等。” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-media-outlets-began-to-pursue-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-past-behavior-including-50000-yen-super-chat-demand-problem/embed/#?secret=N4vK0BOFES#?secret=Z5gzFd4OrL" data-secret="Z5gzFd4OrL" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ujfdGfzC4D"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/">部分摘要网站VTuber 发布怀疑Mirei Gundo的“蓝鲸”行为是否在SNS上传播？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“部分摘要网站 VTuber Gundo Mirei 对‘蓝鲸’行为的怀疑发布在 SNS 上传播了吗？” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/embed/#?secret=4tOhJoKrbD#?secret=ujfdGfzC4D" data-secret="ujfdGfzC4D" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="CrTw9E7gS2"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-news-media-report-on-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mireis-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-this-appears-to-have-appeared-in-nifty-news-and-elsewhere/">一些媒体 Nijisanji 附属的 VTuber Gundo Mirei 报道了涉嫌“蓝鲸”行为的 Nifty News 等。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“一些媒体 Nijisanji 附属的 VTuber Gundo Mirei 报道怀疑“蓝鲸”行为 Nifty 新闻等。”— P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-news-media-report-on-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mireis-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-this-appears-to-have-appeared-in-nifty-news-and-elsewhere/embed/#?secret=mWc7Efwnl1#?secret=CrTw9E7gS2" data-secret="CrTw9E7gS2" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>虽然一些媒体、摘要网站、YouTuber 等对贡多先生过去的行为进行了追究，但大多数批评是基于贡多先生本人的实际所作所为，但基于不明真相的信息。已经做了一些事情，不排除有煽动对军藤先生、虹三治、ANYCOLOR过度攻击的意图的可能性。</p><p>因此，请务必核对人才本人、所在单位、集团或公司发送的一手信息，如发现恶意信息传播或诽谤，请及时向各公司联络点举报。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">也有观点认为，事实上“相当于解除合同”</h3><p>而这次ANYCOLOR宣布军道美玲“毕业”的消息，是基于最初关于WBC的争议言论，前述“过去的问题行为和嫌疑”，以及毕业后SNS将立即关闭的事实。看来，观众和粉丝都在猜测，至少不是顺利毕业，而是接近解约。</p><p> Mirei Gundo 的最终交付将于 6 月 21 日 23:00 举行。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="IRl1hOoWir"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/more-than-2-months-have-passed-since-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-was-suspended-from-activities-by-anycolor/">Nijisanji VTuber Mirei Gundo ANYCOLOR活动中断已经两个多月了</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“自从 Nijisanji 的 VTuber Mirei Gundo 被暂停 ANYCOLOR 活动以来已经过去了 2 个多月” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/more-than-2-months-have-passed-since-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-was-suspended-from-activities-by-anycolor/embed/#?secret=fNBkPMzMx2#?secret=IRl1hOoWir" data-secret="IRl1hOoWir" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/tag/%e9%83%a1%e9%81%93%e7%be%8e%e7%8e%b2/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">&quot;Mirei Gundo&quot;标签的搜索结果</a></p><cite>P2y.jp</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 管理代表“No.2（临时）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙 VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-will-graduate-from-nijisanji-on-june-21/">VTuber Gunimichi Mirei 于 6 月 21 日从 Nijisanji 毕业的</a>帖子首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-will-graduate-from-nijisanji-on-june-21/feed/ 0 94590
